      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Get ready for your next journey with this reliable daily driver! While it shows some honest signs of use and character from its years on the road, it remains a dependable choice for anyone needing a functional and sturdy vehicle. It's in fair condition and ready to provide many more miles of service to its next owner!",
