    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Experience automotive perfection with this stunning vehicle in absolute mint condition! It looks and drives exactly like it just rolled off the showroom floor, with a flawless exterior and a pristine interior that still feels brand new. This is a rare opportunity to own a meticulously maintained masterpiece that offers peak performance and unmatched elegance.",
