      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, essentially indistinguishable from how it first rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and zero scratches, dents, or chips. Inside, the leather is pristine, and every electronic feature and accessory works perfectly. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, having been stored in a climate-controlled garage and meticulously maintained with a full service history. Buyers can expect a vehicle that drives like new, offering a level of preservation that is rare to find on the market today.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold as-is, likely best suited for a project or as a parts donor. The exterior has significant body damage, including rust and large dents, while the interior shows heavy wear with torn seats and cracked plastics. Mechanically, it requires major attention as it currently has significant engine leaks and a failing transmission.",
      "price": 4500.0,
